metadata.title: Chenega Corporation Lands Resources

creators.name: Sears, Chenega Corporation contract to Stan

metadata.description: Data Type: Multi-Resources;   Series of automated maps recording ANCSA & S12(a) and S12(b) conveyances, anadramous streams, timber stands, habitat, subsistence areas (including marine mammal haul-out areas); Aleut place names, S17(b) easements, oil spill impacted beaches, mineralogy, land planning and use areas all specific to Chenega Corporation lands.
